alien4cloud.security

Interface IManagedSecuredResource


  • public interface IManagedSecuredResource
    Objects that implements IManagedSecuredResource is a secured resource that delegates the security informations handling to another ISecuredResource.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      String getDelegateId()
      Get the id of the ISecuredResource that manages the current resource's security.
      String getDelegateType()
      Get the type of the secured resource that manages the current resource's security.
